description: Represents affection or love between two women, with one having a light skin tone. This emoji signifies romantic relationships and deep emotional bonds.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji beautifully depicts two women sharing a tender kiss, rendered with Apple's signature soft, rounded edges and a delicate sense of intimacy. The light skin tone of one woman is subtly highlighted by realistic lighting, showcasing Apple's commitment to nuanced representation. This emoji elegantly symbolizes romantic affection and deep connection between two women, conveying warmth and love in digital conversations.
